### Synchronous Work

##### In the synchronous portion of Module 4, you and your cohort:

* ##### Gained a deeper understanding of how rubrics are used in the CS Discoveries curriculum, and
* ##### Calibrated with your cohort on how to define and measure success in CS Discoveries projects by scoring and discussing a sample student project.

### Asynchronous Work

##### In the asynchronous portion of Module 4, you will:

* ##### Review an upcoming rubric or post-project test for an upcoming unit and
* ##### Consider what you'll need to make sure your students are successful in formative assessment.

##### **Suggested time**: 1 hour
